# Loop Budget — {{REPO_NAME}}

> Token and cost ceiling enforced by C31 before each loop run.
> If any limit is exceeded, the loop HALTS and writes to STATE.md.

## Per-Run Limits

- Max tokens per run: {{BUDGET_TOKENS}}
- Max cost per run: ${{BUDGET_USD}}
- Kill switch: 3 consecutive budget overruns → halt loop entirely

## Daily Limits

- Max tokens per day: {{BUDGET_TOKENS_DAILY}}
- Max cost per day: ${{BUDGET_USD_DAILY}}
- Reset time: 00:00 UTC

## Escalation on Budget Exceeded

1. Write `Budget exceeded: {actual} / {limit} tokens` to STATE.md
2. {{ESCALATION_ACTION}}
3. Halt current run immediately
4. Resume on next scheduled run (do not retry same run)

## Budget Tier: {{BUDGET_TIER}}

| Tier | Per-run | Daily | Strategy |
|------|---------|-------|----------|
| Strict | 3,000 | 15,000 | Report-only, no code changes |
| Standard | 8,000 | 40,000 | Analysis + light fixes |
| Relaxed | 20,000 | 100,000 | Full autonomous execution |

Current tier: **{{BUDGET_TIER}}**

